{"tid":340491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實世界各地既路面電車係點樣買飛","createTime":"2017-07-30T04:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T08:58:21.000Z","uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbae23544a0c005e5ab68d1d728f73bd61fee200","tid":340491,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:01:35.000Z","msg":"香港果個咁既垃圾輕鐵<br />\n根本唔可以100%收足人錢<br />\n實有人搭霸王車<br />\n電車都話好d<br />\n得一出一入<br />\n<br />\n日本果d電車我見廣島果隻都係一出一入<br />\n就算幾卡果d都係兩出兩入左右<br />\n而且有睇住架車既車長<br />\n<br />\n但輕鐵呢d垃圾咁撚多人 係屯元天呢d西地方<br />\n根本無可能做到一出一入 <br />\n<br />\n九鐵起果陣其實係咪預左係咁<br />\n實有人無散紙 張卡無錢 紙幣又買唔到飛<br />\n或者真係唔記得嘟<br />\n<br />\n所以輕鐵真係好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"2ffc344c80debb616f2f666ef6bb783472817231","tid":340491,"uid":6778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:06:52.000Z","msg":"屯元天多垃圾住姐"},{"pid":"8bacfa5099e7193a484cf65522f9912dba798e70","tid":340491,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"多倫多係好似巴士咁上車比$"},{"pid":"8682ec120322ea45b9702e966e8c6caf4874b81f","tid":340491,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"月票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee1388c23c138d035c57c17f7ddf7edcdea927c","tid":340491,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我既意思係點樣check飛"}]}